      "content": "it's just so exhausting to keep up the facade. everyone looks at me and sees a scientist, a scholar, but that person died the moment the error was found. i'm just a walking lie now. there's no \"internal worth\" to find when the entire logic of my life has collapsed. it doesn't feel like a forest without trees, it feels like there shouldn't have been a forest to begin with. i just want the performance to be over.",
